        <Parent_String>Baroque [300021147], Renaissance-Baroque styles and periods [300021031], European [300020656], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
